Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn vampire...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.01,0:00:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jennifer! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.68,0:00:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saved me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.89,0:00:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.02,0:00:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.35,0:00:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A naked girl. What's she doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.40,0:00:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.65,0:00:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It... can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.78,0:00:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoku Gosenzo San'e
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.00,0:00:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.75,0:00:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.96,0:00:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were supposed to be at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.38,0:00:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now isn't the time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.21,0:00:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The vampire's identity is actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.51,0:00:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Itoh-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.73,0:01:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 3: Possessed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.69,0:01:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why Ayumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.53,0:01:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vampires often have limitless superpowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.45,0:01:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Superpowers"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.03,0:01:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, possessing those who've been bitten.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.33,0:01:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moving objects with telekinesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.93,0:01:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It only hurts the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.55,0:01:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jesus!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.02,0:01:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You belong to me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.90,0:01:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she's still nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.90,0:01:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps the vampire that attacked\NAyumi is still in this school?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.53,0:02:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Possibly. At least we can assume the\Nvampire would need to stay nearby,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.91,0:02:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to manipulate the victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.54,0:02:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I'll go find that bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.37,0:02:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.50,0:02:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen, don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.00,0:02:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too dangerous for you. Just go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.42,0:02:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's a bunch of women here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.63,0:02:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of man would I be if I just went home?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.05,0:02:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.09,0:02:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect everyone! Jennifer, Ayumi,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.89,0:02:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you, Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.81,0:02:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.81,0:02:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen, you're a stud. A man's gotta be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.15,0:02:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.28,0:02:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.40,0:02:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.78,0:02:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.62,0:02:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Proceed with extreme caution.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.29,0:02:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.63,0:03:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still don't believe it. A vampire in this school?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.05,0:03:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Schools make good lairs for vampires.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.43,0:03:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.43,0:03:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are plenty of places to hide,\Nand plenty of victims to bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.06,0:03:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Victims...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.89,0:03:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.31,0:03:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Of course I'm not scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.77,0:03:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's all we know for now, Itoh-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.82,0:03:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's asleep at the moment. So don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.95,0:03:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. she'll be fine. Jennifer vill take her home later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.29,0:03:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.29,0:03:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About lunch today...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.79,0:03:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you saying to Ayumi by the pool today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.92,0:03:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.84,0:03:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.63,0:03:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.59,0:03:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was with you during lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.09,0:03:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was after you left
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.22,0:03:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the girls in my class saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi and I were together?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.52,0:03:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.60,0:03:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.31,0:03:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she mistook me for someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.86,0:03:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.03,0:04:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pool, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I just saw something move.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.89,0:04:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vampire...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.89,0:04:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, just the wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.93,0:04:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. When I checked the campus earlier, it was locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.96,0:05:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.40,0:06:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the real Ayumi. No mistaking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.24,0:06:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about the other one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Itoh-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.18,0:06:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.73,0:06:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liz.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.98,0:06:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liz?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.65,0:06:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.53,0:06:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.72,0:07:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.10,0:07:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No. Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.76,0:07:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.06,0:08:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.74,0:08:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.70,0:08:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something just jumped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.37,0:08:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna chase it. Gen, go back without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.71,0:08:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.63,0:08:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if Beth hadn't come, I probably\Nwouldn't have made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.97,0:08:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.55,0:08:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beth! Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.97,0:08:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked her to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.97,0:08:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My duty is to protect the Mistress and Gen-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.73,0:08:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beth...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.86,0:08:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, Gen, you must help Itoh-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.24,0:08:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.16,0:09:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit. She got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.09,0:09:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it disguised itself as Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some vampires have the ability to take on\Nthe appearance of a different person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.06,0:09:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means she wanted to distract us,\Nso she could end up alone with Sakura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we fell for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.36,0:09:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying that Grandma was the\None the vampire wanted all along?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.99,0:09:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liz tasted my blood like she was\Ntrying to discern something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then she smiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.79,0:09:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liz? Is that the vampire's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.63,0:09:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure what her smile meant,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.63,0:09:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there's no mistake: I was her target.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.51,0:10:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Liz? Sounds like a name I've heard before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chemistry Lab
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.82,0:10:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen-sama, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.24,0:10:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd make a barricade.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.49,0:10:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even if you do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it futile?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.00,0:10:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't hold back a vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.33,0:10:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.84,0:10:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.00,0:10:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.59,0:10:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we're all here,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.42,0:10:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she won't materialize into this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.76,0:10:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.97,0:10:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vampires are actually quite insecure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.01,0:10:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.72,0:10:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason they change forms and hide in\Nthe dark is not just to attack humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.03,0:10:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because they are outcasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.95,0:11:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, everyone. Let's all take a little rest here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.83,0:11:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we have a midnight snack?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.67,0:11:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't fight on empty stomachs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.21,0:11:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.05,0:11:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The epitome of the Japanese warrior:\N"Never eat, never sleep!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.22,0:11:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.30,0:11:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yum!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.35,0:11:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat as much as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.10,0:11:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.85,0:11:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seemed a little strange at first, but you\Nlook really cute in that school uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.19,0:11:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.25,0:11:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.42,0:12:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.05,0:12:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.76,0:12:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen, I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.30,0:12:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.06,0:12:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.44,0:12:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.07,0:12:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.18,0:12:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.45,0:13:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.99,0:13:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.45,0:13:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go wash my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.83,0:13:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he's really wiped.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.10,0:13:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.68,0:13:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking at the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.73,0:13:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.73,0:13:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moon appears with the night\Nand disappears with the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.65,0:13:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its form is ever-changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.53,0:13:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're quite similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.03,0:13:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You used the word "outcast" back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.08,0:13:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even an outcast can cast\Nsparkling light on many people...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.92,0:14:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just like that full moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.63,0:14:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago, my Mistress told me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.63,0:14:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My grandma did?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.30,0:14:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.47,0:14:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I finally believe it wholeheartedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.06,0:14:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'll be off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.11,0:14:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I explained everything to her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.98,0:14:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you get there, please contact us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.49,0:14:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Gen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.24,0:14:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.75,0:14:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I feared, Liz is too powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.54,0:14:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must finish this tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.00,0:14:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beth,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.92,0:14:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you always seem to suffer on my behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.26,0:14:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all, Mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.47,0:14:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protecting both you and Gen-sama is my privilege.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.60,0:14:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not consider it a burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.64,0:15:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If l am of help to you, then I can\Natone for the evil in my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beth...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.35,0:15:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But more importantly, Mistress...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.15,0:15:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are you sure it is entirely wise to destroy Liz?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.11,0:15:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you want to use vampire genes\Nto help cure Gen-sama's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I had thought of that at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.24,0:15:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But luckily, Gen's condition is improving.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.46,0:15:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think his current medication is sufficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.17,0:15:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wish to take the risk of letting Liz live.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.63,0:15:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mistress, is that what you truly feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.18,0:15:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe you feel the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.81,0:15:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The opposite?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.31,0:15:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To use the vampire's powers to restore\NGen-sama's immortal body to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.23,0:15:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To completely resurrect–
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.40,0:15:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beth!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.53,0:16:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have only one wish: to let Gen lead a normal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.87,0:16:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.71,0:16:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.63,0:16:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.60,0:16:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Ayumi was shut up in there during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.56,0:16:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.77,0:16:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vampires can't walk around in broad daylight, can they?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.03,0:16:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means that someone else\Nmust have taken Ayumi there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.00,0:16:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Could it be... Jennifer? No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.76,0:16:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'm going back to the classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.97,0:17:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.06,0:17:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.02,0:17:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not "hear".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.65,0:17:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't "hear" anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.41,0:17:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The noises outside have no sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.75,0:17:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems as though we are trapped in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.30,0:17:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.46,0:17:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps it would be easier to\Nunderstand if I lowered the barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.97,0:17:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this Liz's doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.30,0:17:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.43,0:17:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must contact Jennifer at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.56,0:17:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.35,0:17:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the reason for trapping us in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.19,0:17:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, so that we couldn't run away if we were attacked?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.16,0:18:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it. It's to prevent us from getting in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.04,0:18:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that means, Liz's true target is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.04,0:18:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen's in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.73,0:18:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jennifer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you... Liz?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.84,0:18:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.59,0:18:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For your blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.26,0:19:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.09,0:19:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.02,0:19:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Cut that out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.65,0:19:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say you wanted my blood!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.30,0:19:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,J-Jennifer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Snap out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.05,0:19:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jennifer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.32,0:20:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beth!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.58,0:20:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mistress...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.91,0:20:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! While there's still time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.83,0:20:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beth!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.21,0:21:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.26,0:21:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I'm coming... too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.53,0:22:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liz!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.54,0:22:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.25,0:22:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.75,0:22:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. He wasn't bitten.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.05,0:22:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want blood!? Then take mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.93,0:22:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.10,0:22:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't die anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.77,0:22:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if you cut me to pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.35,0:22:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you lay a finger on Gen!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.49,0:22:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hinder me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.28,0:22:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this man by my side, I have no need of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.75,0:23:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.30,0:23:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.03,0:23:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.85,0:23:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.43,0:23:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Destroyed" is a better word.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.72,0:24:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vampires do not die.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.48,0:24:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beth...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.56,0:24:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was for the best. This was...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.75,0:24:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.00,0:24:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see. Are you okay now?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.21,0:24:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.88,0:24:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.55,0:24:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.89,0:24:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yoshino.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.89,0:24:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen you in three days, Ayumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.14,0:24:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened? I was worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.81,0:24:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I was just exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.31,0:24:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should probably take up skipping class like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.98,0:24:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.19,0:24:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I was just joking. Don't take me seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.08,0:25:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap. We're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.79,0:25:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.08,0:25:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.58,0:25:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.92,0:25:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.98,0:26:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, on Zoku Gosenzou San'e:
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.73,0:26:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remnants of a Dream.
